Comment: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My... My hair!
Comment: 0,0:00:13.72,0:00:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hair... Let me eat more!
Comment: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hair!
Comment: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ameno School Demon-slaying Ninjutsu,\Nsecret technique! Evening Late Autumn Shower!
Comment: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Urara, can you hear me?
Comment: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mission complete.\NI disposed of the hair-eater.
Comment: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's my Sagiri!\NYou always complete the missions quickly.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, so about the next job...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hear a spirit medium boy\Nmoved in to your place.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi Fuyuzora. What about him?
Comment: 0,0:00:56.85,0:01:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}There is a group of psychic ninjas who use\Nsecret techniques to carry out divine punishment{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}against cruel, violent youkai who do wrong\Nto humans under the cover of night.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}They call themselves the Chuuma Ninja Army.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:49.00,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri is Watching Youkai!
Comment: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There's Sagiri!
Comment: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's she doing here?
Comment: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's a first-year student like you, right?
Comment: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's the first I've heard.
Comment: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you curious about her?
Comment: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ameno is a very beautiful girl,\Nbut I'd give up if I were you.
Comment: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why?
Comment: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She came to my middle school\Nwhen I was in the second year.
Comment: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,At that time, she was the topic\Nof every conversation.
Comment: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's beautiful, and great in academics\Nand athletics. A perfect superhuman had arrived!
Comment: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Perfect?
Comment: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But with her amazing physical strength\Nand male-hating personality,
Comment: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,she soon had every boy in school terrified!
Comment: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Comment: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri had been going to an all-girl’s school since\Nkindergarten, so she's probably not used to boys.
Comment: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi Fuyuzora.
Comment: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you have a minute? I want to talk to you.
Comment: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Talk?
Comment: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You know Ameno?
Comment: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There are too many eyes here.
Comment: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Follow me to the roof.
Comment: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What did you want to tell me?
Comment: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A-Actually...
Comment: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Comment: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um... Well...
Comment: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Uh...
Comment: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You see...
Comment: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What is it?
Comment: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is not my intention.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's true that there's no one else\Nwho would be suitable.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Going by what I hear from Yuuna,\Nit seems you're somewhat talented!
Comment: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi Fuyuzora!
Comment: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Since you're a spirit medium, as a Chuuma Ninja,\NI want to hire you for an assignment!
Comment: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The job is to help me hunt down a youkai.
Comment: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:49.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's dangerous though,\Nso Yuuna can't come along. Okay?
Comment: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay. Please be careful, you two!
Comment: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hunting down youkai, huh?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is the enemy so powerful\Nthat Sagiri doesn't stand a chance against it?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyway, why did she want to meet here?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, you're really cute.
Comment: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Come hang out with us.
Comment: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Um, but...
Comment: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Want to go karaoke?
Comment: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, it's settled.
Comment: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey! You're obviously troubling her.
Comment: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't you dare touch me so easily!
Comment: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri?
Comment: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're here, Kogarashi Fuyuzora.
Comment: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You have low tolerance in public too, huh?
Comment: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}First, change into this.
Comment: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sure.
Comment: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Currently, there's been a spate of incidents\Nof young couples
Comment: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}coming to this park at night and being attacked\Nby a black fog, so now the park's shut down.
Comment: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Black fog?
Comment: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,After doing a spirit vision in the Chuuma village,\Nit was determined that it's the work of a youkai.
Comment: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The victims are always a couple, so I asked\Nfor your cooperation to lure the youkai out.
Comment: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Makes sense.
Comment: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So are the victims okay?
Comment: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The victims...
Comment: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,had their clothes melted by the black fog,\Nand left completely naked.
Comment: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:39.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a new kind of youkai that likes to eat\Npheromone-stained fibers.
Comment: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That kind of youkai exists?
Comment: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It does, which is why we're here!
Comment: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So that's why\Nyou had me change clothes too, huh?
Comment: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So is there a force field or something\Non these clothes so they can't get eaten?
Comment: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, because then it wouldn't be bait.
Comment: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,These are regular clothes.
Comment: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then...
Comment: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,won't the two of us become stark naked?
Comment: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wha...
Comment: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bastard, what were you imagining?
Comment: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can tell?
Comment: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'm surprised\Nyou asked for my help for this kind of mission.
Comment: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I told you, it wasn't my intention.
Comment: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,However, a youkai that's a danger to humans,
Comment: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and worse, it humiliates women and girls,\Nso I couldn't just let it go.
Comment: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For that sake, I'm determined to be\Na Chuuma ninja before being a woman.
Comment: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Therefore I won't balk at asking you for help\Nor even being stripped naked.
Comment: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I understand the situation.
Comment: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So let's go lure out that youkai.
Comment: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm counting on you.
Comment: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No sign of it yet, huh?
Comment: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe it sensed your murderous intent\Nand is too afraid to come out.
Comment: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That could be true.
Comment: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If the black fog doesn't appear,\Nit's probably because I'm not feminine enough.
Comment: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,With this outfit,\NI did my best to look more feminine,
Comment: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}but it must not suit a body\Nthat's been trained for battle.
Comment: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}But if that is the case,\Nthen this operation will fail.
Comment: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Do you have any ideas?
Comment: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, let's see.
Comment: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Want to try walking arm in arm?
Comment: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The black fog attacks couples, right?
Comment: 0,0:08:57.03,0:09:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So I thought maybe\Nwe should try appearing like that.
Comment: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that wouldn't work anyway.
Comment: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, it’s worth a try.
Comment: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,O-Oh? Then want to try linking arms?
Comment: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why so violent?
Comment: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}There it is!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So this is the fog that melts fibers.
Comment: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The main body\Nthat's producing this fog is nearby.
Comment: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- We need to find it!\N- Right!
Comment: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I didn't think there would be\Nthis much black fog in the area.
Comment: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh no, when did it...
Comment: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My clothes are melting faster than I expected!
Comment: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I need to hurry.
Comment: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looks like the source of this fog is over there.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think I'll get a little serious.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}He blew away the fog with the force of his fist?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just how haphazard is Kogarashi Fuyuzora?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}You bastard, what are you?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So that's the black fog's true form!
Comment: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Be careful, Sagiri!
Comment: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Take this!
Comment: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ameno School Demon-slaying Ninjutsu,\Nsecret technique!
Comment: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rain Storm!
Comment: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri!
Comment: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Comment: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Comment: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi Fuyuzora!
Comment: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Y-You were a big help this time. I'm grateful.
Comment: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Think nothing of it.
Comment: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Our clothes are in tatters, huh?
Comment: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Comment: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They didn't really suit me anyway.
Comment: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You think so?
Comment: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought you actually looked cute in that outfit.
Comment: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wha...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you...\NWh-What do you mean, calling me cute?
Comment: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's nothing, really. Come on, let's go home.
Comment: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}For a few days afterward...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}A-As an experiment,\Nshould I wear this normally?{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it just isn't me...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sagiri was in anguish in front of the mirror.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:12:24.41,0:12:27.74,Title2,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri is Cautious
Comment: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, Yaya!
Comment: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's wake up already!
Comment: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's dangerous for you to be sleeping there!
Comment: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's time for lunch!
Comment: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Food.
Comment: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya!
Comment: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you, Cat God.
Comment: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cat God?
Comment: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's in the nature of cat gods\Nto protect their host.
Comment: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nature?
Comment: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cat gods whimsically possess a human\Nand then give that host various powers.
Comment: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To the Chuuma Ninja Army, they're basically\Nacknowledged as harmless youkai.
Comment: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But why did it possess Yaya?
Comment: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because we're friends.
Comment: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's all?
Comment: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Apparently it's usually sleeping inside Yaya,
Comment: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but you can often see it playing\Nwhen it comes out of her, too.
Comment: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,From the way it always returns to her, though,\Nyou can tell it loves Yaya.
Comment: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- More!\N- Sure.
Comment: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm so happy that I get to eat\NMs. Nakai's delicious cooking every day!
Comment: 0,0:13:58.38,0:13:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That appreciation makes it all worthwhile\Nto cook for everyone.
Comment: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,By the way, I'm leaving tomorrow for\Nthe Hot Spring Association's annual trip.
Comment: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Will everyone be okay?
Comment: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Of course. We're planning\Nto split the cooking duties.
Comment: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We'll be fine for two or three days.
Comment: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please have a good time!
Comment: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You deserve to relax once in a while, Ms. Nakai.
Comment: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Comment: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you! Then if everyone will be okay...
Comment: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so the tenants saw\NMs. Nakai off with good cheer, but...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Breakfast is ready!
Comment: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}CAT FOOD\NTUNA
Comment: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's this?
Comment: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Breakfast.
Comment: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}CAT FOOD\NTUNA\NYOUR CAT WILL SWOON!!
Comment: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It says "canned cat food"!
Comment: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,At least prepare canned food\Nthat humans can eat!
Comment: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But this one's yummy.
Comment: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dinnertime, everyone!
Comment: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}POTATO CHIPS\NSEAWEED SALT\NCORN
Comment: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, eat up!
Comment: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the first day,\Neveryone ached for Ms. Nakai's return.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It looks delicious!
Comment: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Finally, a decent meal!
Comment: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who made it?
Comment: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I did!
Comment: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna, really?
Comment: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even though you're a ghost,\Nyou can cook, too?
Comment: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal!
Comment: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Comment: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yuuna mistook vinegar for cooking sake,\Nand cola for soy sauce.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unless an offering is made to her,\Nshe doesn't know how something tastes.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal.
Comment: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It seems I'm the only one\Nwho can actually cook.
Comment: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}RUMBLE RUMBLE RUMBLE
Comment: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is the Ameno School's secret wild plant curry\Nwith natural medicine mixed in!
Comment: 0,0:15:55.99,0:16:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The medicinal roots are bitter and have\Na peculiar odor, but it's the ultimate healthy dish!
Comment: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is everyone okay?
Comment: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}That peculiar odor\Nturned out to be too peculiar.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Salt-grilled salmon!
Comment: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It looks like it's shining with a golden aura!
Comment: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-It's too good!
Comment: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Finally delicious food!
Comment: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Even though it's on a skewer, it looks like\Nit's still alive, and the way it was cooked is divine!
Comment: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't imagine any human\Nhaving the skill to do this!
Comment: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who could possibly...
Comment: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I did.
Comment: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi?
Comment: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Three years to learn skewering,\Nand a lifetime to grill...
Comment: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There was a legendary artisan who perfected\Nthe ultimate grilling technique right as he died,
Comment: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and he wanted to leave it for posterity.
Comment: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That ghost possessed me for a while\Nand made me train.
Comment: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're beyond amazing, Kogarashi!
Comment: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've never had fish like this before!
Comment: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi,\Nthis fish goes wonderfully with booze!
Comment: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So I've been defeated.
Comment: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi everyone, I'm back!
Comment: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hooray! Hooray!
Comment: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's the fuss about?
Comment: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Ms. Nakai!
Comment: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Welcome home!\N- Welcome home.
Comment: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm back, everyone.
Comment: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- How was your trip?\N- Were you able to relax?
Comment: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks to you.
Comment: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Where's my souvenir, Ms. Nakai?\N- Yeah, souvenirs!
Comment: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, don't push! Don't push!
Comment: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next day...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Did something happen with those two?
Comment: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NThey've been like that since this morning.
Comment: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya! Can I help you with something?
Comment: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So what can I do for you?
Comment: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}And so, for some reason,{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yaya continued to follow Kogarashi around.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Scenic Open-Air Hot Spring
Comment: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sheesh. What's up with Yaya?
Comment: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Even though\Nshe was never curious about me before.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}But I'm sure she'd never come here.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya?
Comment: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya will wash your back.
Comment: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Comment: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hot!
Comment: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry! Are you okay?
Comment: 0,0:18:58.26,0:18:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Comment: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why is this happening?
Comment: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Does this hurt?
Comment: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nah. It's no big deal.
Comment: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, it was my fault too, so don't worry about it.
Comment: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya's not very good with hot water.
Comment: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So much that she checks the temperature\Nof the bath several times before getting in.
Comment: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}CAUTIOUS
Comment: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:35.01,RightSign,NTP,0,0,0,,CAUTIOUS
Comment: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She really is like a cat.
Comment: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You've been acting weird\Nsince the day before yesterday.
Comment: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What's up?
Comment: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If I recall, the day before that\Nwas when Kogarashi cooked for us.
Comment: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My cooking?
Comment: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe you want to eat my grilled fish again?
Comment: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Comment: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She could've just said so from the beginning.
Comment: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, in her own way, Yaya is concerned\Nwith keeping proper distance from other people.
Comment: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She hasn't known you long, so it was probably\Nhard for her to ask you for a favor.
Comment: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I see.
Comment: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya!
Comment: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here, it's ready.
Comment: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you eat all this?
Comment: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And you told me not to put salt on it?
Comment: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Because I heard\Ncats shouldn't have too much salt.
Comment: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that true for you, too?
Comment: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya prefers it with salt, but...
Comment: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wanted Cat God to be able to eat it, too.
Comment: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That means it's delicious.
Comment: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. So she was doing her best for Cat God.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kogarashi.
Comment: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Will you grill fish for me again?
Comment: 0,0:21:32.33,0:21:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sure!
Comment: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that, once in a while,\NYaya could be seen following Kogarashi around.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He's taming her with food.
Comment: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next time: Yuuna's Body Measurements\Nand Nonko's Crunch Time
Comment: 0,0:23:36.62,0:23:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Don't miss...
Comment: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,the next episode!
Comment: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.21,0:00:11.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,T-Tóc của tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.72,0:00:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tóc, cho ta ăn tóc nữa đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tóc!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:25.93,Ninjutsu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fscy0\t(0,300,\fscy106)\fad(200,300)\pos(960,1000)}Nhẫn pháp Trừ yêu phái Ameno, bí kỹ! Tiểu dạ Thời vũ!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:39.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Urara, nghe thấy tớ không?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhiệm vụ hoàn tất.\NXử xong con yêu quái ăn tóc rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:46.04,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Không hổ danh Sagiri, hoàn thành nhiệm vụ nhanh ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:48.71,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,À còn việc tiếp theo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:53.09,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nghe nói có một nam linh lực giả mới chuyển tới chỗ cậu à?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora Kogarashi, tên đó thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.56,0:01:02.23,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fscy0\t(0,300,\fscy106)\fad(200,000}Có một tập đoàn nhẫn giả ẩn mình trong bóng đêm trừng trị kẻ ác và bọn yêu quái bạo ngược,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:08.69,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,sở hữu trong mình những bí kỹ linh diệu gọi là "Thiên Tru".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:13.61,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Họ tự xưng là Trừ ma Nhẫn quân.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.17,0:02:49.00,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,00)}Theo dấu yêu quái ! Sagiri-san
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri-san kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.84,0:02:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sao Sagiri lại ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri-san cũng là học sinh năm nhất như Kogarashi-san kia mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mới nghe luôn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chú tò mò về nhỏ ấy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đúng là Ameno chuẩn kiểu mỹ nhân, nhưng nếu anh là chú thì anh đã thôi mơ mộng nhỏ ấy rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.52,0:03:15.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hồi anh còn học lớp 8 thì nhỏ ấy chuyển tới trường cấp hai của anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hồi đó nhỏ ấy trở thành chủ đề bàn tán luôn đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nét người yêu kiều, văn võ song toàn, thành tích xuất sắc, chuẩn kiểu người hoàn hảo luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hoàn hảo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:30.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng chẳng mấy chốc, thể lực quỷ thần và tính căm ghét đàn ông của nhỏ ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,đã khiến tất cả đám con trai trong trường kinh sợ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:35.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À, rồi rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Từ khi còn mẫu giáo Sagiri-san đã học ở trường toàn nữ sinh, chắc do vậy nên cậu ấy không quen học chung với con trai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora Kogarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Giờ rảnh không? Ta nói chuyện chút.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:49.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nói chuyện?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.06,0:03:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chú quen Ameno à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.98,0:03:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ở đây có quá nhiều người.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Theo ta lên sân thượng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chuyện gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,T-Thật ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À thì, chuyện là...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chuyện là...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rốt cuộc là chuyện gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:18.76,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Đây không phải là ý định của mình!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:23.22,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng đúng là ngoài tên này ra thì không có ai khác hợp cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.55,0:04:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Theo như lời Yuuna nói, thì nhà ngươi khá là có tài ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora Kogarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vì ngươi là linh lực giả, nên với tư cách nhẫn giả trừ ma, ta muốn thuê ngươi làm 1 chuyện!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:44.41,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Việc của ngươi là hỗ trợ ta xử lý 1 con yêu quái.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:49.24,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Vì công việc rất nguy hiểm, nên Yuuna không được đi theo, rõ chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:51.79,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng, vậy 2 người cẩn thận nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:54.25,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Xử lý yêu quái à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:58.17,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Kẻ địch mạnh đến nỗi Sagiri không thể tự mình tiêu diệt à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:02.76,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Cơ mà, sao nhỏ ấy lại muốn hẹn gặp ở đây nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nè nè, em gì ơi, dễ thương quá ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đi chơi với bọn anh nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy đi karaoke nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chốt rồi nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.10,0:05:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Này, mấy người đang làm phiền cô ấy đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đừng có tự ý chạm vào ta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.07,0:05:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tới rồi à, Fuyuzora Kogarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ở nơi công cộng cậu cũng chẳng nương tay chút nào nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:35.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trước tiên, thay cái này đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hiện công viên này đã bị đóng cửa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:10.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,do xảy ra vụ một làn sương mù đen tấn công những cặp đôi trẻ tới đây vào ban đêm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sương mù đen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Theo kết quả từ linh thị của làng Trừ ma, thì vụ này là do yêu quái gây ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vì những người bị hại đều là những cặp đôi, nên ta mới cần ngươi giúp sức để dụ nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ra là vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy những người bị hại có sao không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Những người bị hại...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:32.76,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Không~!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quần áo của họ bị làn sương đen làm cho biến mất, kết quả là không còn mảnh vải che thân.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:39.27,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Không~!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xem ra nó là loại yêu quái mới thích ăn các loại sợi màu pheromone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có cả loại yêu quái đó nữa à?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thì do có nó nên hai ta mới tới đây đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế nên cậu mới bắt tui thay đồ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.78,0:06:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy tức là bộ đồ này có kết giới bao quanh hay thứ gì đó mà nó không ăn được à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không, nếu vậy thì nó sẽ không ăn đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đây chỉ là đồ bình thường thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:03.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,không phải 2 ta cũng phải chịu cảnh trần như nhộng sao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhà ngươi tưởng tượng cái gì đó hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Biết rồi còn hỏi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cơ mà được Sagiri nhờ giúp một nhiệm vụ thế này thì có hơi bất giờ đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đã nói không phải ta muốn thế mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng mà, loại yêu quái có thể gây nguy hiểm tới con người,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,hay nghiêm trọng hơn là làm ô nhục thanh danh phụ nữ, thì không thể bỏ qua được.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế nên, ta đã quyết định trở thành nhẫn giả trừ ma trước khi làm phụ nữ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nên là, dù có phải nhờ ngươi giúp, hay là chịu cảnh trần truồng ta cũng không từ!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hiểu sự tình rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.55,0:07:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy, cùng đi lôi cổ con yêu quái đó ra ánh sáng nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ừ, nhờ cả vào ngươi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:09.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chưa thấy nó xuất hiện nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hay là nó cảm nhận được sát khí của cậu nên chạy mất dép rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Biết đâu vậy cũng nên.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu làn sương đen không xuất hiện, thì có lẽ là do ta không đủ nữ tính rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ta ăn mặc thế này, cốt là cố để trông nữ tính hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng xem ra nó không hợp với cơ thể từng kinh qua chiến trận này rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng nếu không làm thế thì kế hoạch này sẽ đổ vỡ mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngươi có cách nào không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải rồi nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy thì, tay trong tay cùng nhau đi bộ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Làn sương đen tấn công những cặp đôi mà phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:09:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy thì chúng ta chỉ cần cư xử sao cho giống như thế là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.67,0:09:06.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mà chắc cách đó cũng chẳng ăn thua đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không, cũng đáng để thử...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,T-Thế à? Vậy ta thử xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mạnh tay quá vậy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:34.20,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Tới rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đây là làn sương làm vải tan biến à.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bổn thể tạo ra làn sương này đang ở gần đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải tìm cho được nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không ngờ làn sương đen ở đây lại dày đặc tới vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.93,0:09:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Từ khi nào mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.43,0:09:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quần áo tan biến nhanh hơn mình tưởng!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phải nhanh lên thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:04.06,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Không ổn rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:08.44,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Xem ra thứ tạo ra làn sương này ở bên đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:11.57,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Chắc phải nghiêm túc tí thôi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:23.50,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Thổi tan làn sương chỉ với 1 cú đấm ư?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:27.29,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngươi mạnh đến cỡ nào vậy, Fuyuzora Kogarashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.88,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhà ngươi, rốt cuộc là thứ gì?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ra đó là bản thể của làn sương đen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.43,0:10:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cẩn thận, Sagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đỡ này!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:52.36,Ninjutsu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fscy0\t(0,300,\fscy106)\fad(200,300)\pos(960,1000)}Nhẫn pháp Trừ yêu phái Ameno, bí kỹ!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:54.80,Ninjutsu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2\fscy0\t(0,300,\fscy106)\fad(200,300)\pos(960,1000)}Bạo Vũ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không sao chứ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,X-Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Fuyuzora Kogarashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:26.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,L-Lần này may có ngươi, xin cảm tạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.06,0:11:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Quần áo rách hết rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.32,0:11:38.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dù gì chúng cũng có hợp với ta đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:42.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tui thì nghĩ cậu ăn mặc thế nhìn đáng yêu lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-N-N-Nhà ngươi, n-nói người ta đáng yêu, ý là sao hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không có gì, nào, mình về thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:01.34,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Những ngày sau đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:07.06,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,C-Có nên mặc bộ này vào ngày thường không nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:11.56,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Không, quả nhiên mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.65,0:12:18.07,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,...Sagiri cứ đứng soi gương rồi dằn vặt suốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:27.73,Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,00)\an1}Yaya, rụt rù rụt rè
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nè, Yaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mau dậy đi em.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngủ trên đó nguy hiểm lắm đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tới giờ ăn trưa rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.72,0:12:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đồ ăn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.66,0:13:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn Người, Miêu Thần!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miêu Thần là...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.38,0:13:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Miêu Thần hay có tập tính bảo vệ chủ nhân của chúng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tập tính?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.67,0:13:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Các Miêu Thần hay chọn con người làm chủ nhân, sau đó dựa vào bản chất của mỗi người để trao cho họ sức mạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Với Trừ ma Nhẫn đội bọn ta, thì về cơ bản, chúng không được xem là yêu quái.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.51,0:13:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng sao nó lại chọn đi theo Yaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vì bọn em thân với nhau mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.06,0:13:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhiêu đó thôi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hình như nó hay ngủ trong người Yaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.32,0:13:44.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nhưng khi nó ra bên ngoài thì vẫn có thể thấy được.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chỉ là lúc nào nó cũng về bên Yaya, nên có thể nói nó thích con bé cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Cho bát nữa!\N- Có ngay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thật hạnh phúc khi ngày nào cũng được ăn đồ ngon do Nakai-san nấu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.84,0:14:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nghe mọi người nói vậy khiến chị muốn làm thêm ghê!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nói mới nhớ, mai chị phải tham gia chuyến du lịch thường niên của Hiệp hội Suối nước nóng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không biết để mấy đứa ở nhà có ổn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dĩ nhiên, bọn em sẽ lên kế hoạch chia nhau ra nấu ăn mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu chỉ vài ba ngày thì không sao đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chúc chị đi vui vẻ nhé!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lâu lâu cũng phải để Nakai-san xả hơi chứ nhể.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.78,0:14:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn mọi người, vậy nếu không còn chuyện gì nữa thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:37.46,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế là, những vị khách thuê trọ tiễn Nakai-san đi trong không khí rất vui vẻ, có điều...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bữa sáng xong rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:42.59,Sign,NTP,0,0,0,,ĐỒ ĂN CHO MÈO\NTUNA
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đây là?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bữa sáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trên đó ghi "thức ăn đóng lon cho mèo" đấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chí ít em cũng chọn được loại đồ ăn đóng lon dành cho người chứ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng cái này ngon lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mọi người, bữa tối xong rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:15:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nào, ăn nhiệt tình vào!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:08.91,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Sau ngày đầu tiên, ai cũng mong ngóng Nakai-san về cả...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhìn ngon ghê!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.37,0:15:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cuối cùng cũng được ăn 1 bữa đàng hoàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:16.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Là ai nấu thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.37,0:15:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình nấu đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Là ma nhưng vẫn có thể nấu ăn được à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mời cả nhà dùng!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mình xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:37.31,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Yuuna đã bỏ nhầm giấm và cô-ca thay vì rượu và xì dầu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:42.52,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Nếu không được cúng thì cô ấy chẳng biết vị của chúng ra sao đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn vì bữa ăn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xem ra chỉ có mình tớ nấu được thôi ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.74,0:15:55.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đây là món cà-ry bí truyền của phái Ameno sử dụng hỗn hợp thảo dược tự nhiên!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:16:01.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tuy những lương dược này có vị đắng và mùi rất độc đáo, nhưng món ăn này cực kỳ tốt cho sức khoẻ!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mọi người có sao không?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:11.18,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Mùi độc đáo ấy, quả đúng là rất "độc"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cá hồi nướng muối!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:19.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Toả sáng như ánh hào quang ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N-Ngon bá cháy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cuối cùng cũng được ăn đồ ngon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cứ như chúng vẫn còn sống dù bị xiên, và cả cách nướng cũng rất thần thánh nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không ngờ lại có người đạt được đẳng cấp này!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rốt cuộc là...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tui làm đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:41.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:45.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Học xiên 3 năm, nướng cả đời.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.75,0:16:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Từng có một đầu bếp huyền thoại đã hoàn thành bí kỹ nướng cá ngay trước khi chết,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:51.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,và ông ấy muốn truyền lại cho hậu thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.97,0:16:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hồn ma từng ám tớ ấy đã chỉ dạy cho tớ đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cậu ghê lắm luôn đó, Kogarashi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đây là lần đầu em được ăn món cá ngon như này đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarash-chan, món này mà nhậu chung với rượu thì nhất luôn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.94,0:17:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế này thì ta bái phục rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:11.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mọi người, chị về rồi đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có chuyện gì mà huyên náo thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ô, Nakai-san kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mừng chị về!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Chị về rồi đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Chuyến du lịch thế nào?\N- Chị nghỉ xả hơi được chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vâng, cảm ơn mấy đứa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:33.59,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngày tiếp theo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hai đứa bị sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em không biết nữa, sáng giờ họ cứ vậy suốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:59.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya! Cần anh giúp gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À, rốt cuộc là cần anh làm gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:13.21,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Và, không hiểu vì sao mà Yaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.21,0:18:19.39,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,cứ bám theo Kogarashi suốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.43,0:18:26.52,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Thiệt là, Yaya bị gì thế không biết?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:30.65,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Trước giờ con bé có hứng thú với mình đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:34.24,Default - Italics,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhưng chắc không có chuyện con bé vào đây đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Để Yaya kỳ lưng cho anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.45,0:18:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em nói cái gì vậy hả?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.66,0:18:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nóng!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.62,0:18:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi, em có sao không!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:18:59.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:05.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sao lại thành ra thế này chứ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có đau lắm không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không đau lắm đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kogarashi, xin lỗi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,À không, anh cũng có lỗi mà, đừng để bụng.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya-san không thích nước nóng cho lắm,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,nên em ấy hay kiểm tra nhiệt độ bể tắm vài lần trước khi vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.30,0:19:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Đúng là giống mèo thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.63,0:19:39.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Từ hôm trước tới giờ em lạ lắm đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.26,0:19:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có chuyện gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hình như hôm trước là ngày Kogarashi-san nấu cho bọn mình ăn nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.56,0:19:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ngày tớ nấu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Không lẽ em muốn ăn món cá nướng của anh nữa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:04.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thiệt tình.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Có mỗi chuyện đó thì nói thẳng từ đầu là được rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mà Yaya rất chú ý tới việc giữ khoảng cách với người khác.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vì chưa quen ngươi lâu nên chuyện nhờ vả ngươi với con bé rất khó.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Xong rồi này.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ăn có hết đống này không thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Còn bảo anh đừng thêm muối vào nữa chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:54.38,Sign,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be2}Nếu mèo ăn quá mặn sẽ bị rối loạn các chất điện giải, viêm thận, tiết niệu, bí đái, có thể dẫn đến tử vong
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em nghe nói mèo không nên ăn nhiều muối mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya cũng bị thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yaya thích ăn cá nướng với muối hơn, nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Em muốn Miêu Thần cũng ăn được nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.94,0:21:16.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ý ngài ấy là ngon lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vậy ra con bé cố đến thế là vì Miêu Thần à?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn nhé, Kogarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lần sau nướng cá cho em ăn nữa nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.39,0:21:56.94,Default - Flashback,NTP,0,0,0,,Thế là, thỉnh thoảng, Yaya lại bám theo Kogarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hắn ta dùng đồ ăn để thuần hoá con bé kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:40.04,Next Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\blur3}SỐ ĐO CƠ THỂ CỦA YUUNA-SAN\NNONKO-SAN TRONG THẾ NGẶT NGHÈO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.62,0:23:37.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nhớ đón xem...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,tập tiếp theo nhé!
